name: Booking a service with >24h duration - client's place

steps.name: Input search text and press Enter
$("app-search form input") set value("Investor Factors Facilitator (uh78ccv)")
Verify that the search result is correct
$("app-search-result ion-card-content app-service-link") should have(text "Investor Factors Facilitator (uh78ccv)")
Verify that the service data is correct
$("app-service-widget") should have(text "Keep Summer safe. The road goes ever on and on")

parameters.name: serviceDescription
parameters.value: Keep Summer safe. The road goes ever on and on

steps.name: $("app-service-widget/app-service-location") should have([text "Russia", text "Moscow", text "8483 Trang Square, Swiftfort, CT 76592"])
$("app-service-widget") should have(text "Ordering of this service will be approved automatically")
$("app-book div.calendar/with text: 4") should have([css class "selected", 10 s.])
$("app-confirmation-step div.footer ion-button") should not have([css class "button-disabled", 10 s.])
$("app-confirmation-step div.footer ion-button") should not be([visible, 10 s.])
